<!DOCTYPE>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Verify Your Account</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body style="background-color: #F5F5F5; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
     <p style="float: right;"> <%= image_tag attachments['lingoamojr.png'].url %> </p>
     <br>
    <h3 style="color: #333333; text-align: left;"><strong>Email Verification</strong></h3>
    <p style="color: #333333;text-align: center;"><strong>Hi, <%= @teacher.first_name %> </strong></p>
<p style="color: #333333;text-align: center;"><strong>You're almost ready to start teaching a new language<br> with Lingoamo. Click on the button to verify your<br> email:</strong></p>
<br>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
      <a href="<%= @url %>" style="background-color:#6D5996 ; color: #FFFFFF; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 100px; border-radius: 5px;">Verify email</a>
    </div>
<br>
    <p style="color: #333333;text-align: center;"><strong>The Lingoamo team</strong></p>   
  </div>
</body>
</html>